olitics in American government.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aExecutive powerzUnited States. 0aPresidentsxLegal status, laws, etczUnited States. 0aPresidentsxLegal status, laws, etc.zUnited States. 7aLAW / Constitutional.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030012351740uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030017801240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300178012423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300178012/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY